<div class='row'>
  <div class='large-6 columns' >
    <h1>Wingtags</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="main-content">
  <div class="row centered-text">
    <div class="large-6 columns">
      <p>The purpose of the Wingtags Project is to understand how Sulphur-crested Cockatoos have adapted to living in the highly urban environment of Sydney by using crowdsourced reports from people like you.</p>
      <p>Learn more ⟶</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="main-content">
  <div class="row centered-text">
    <div class="large-6 columns">
